title: DAN MORGENSTERN RECALLS KENNY DORHAM (Dec. 14, 2018)
description: Dan Morgenstern, Jazz Eminence, recalls the great trumpeter, composer, and writer Kenny Dorham, in a conversation at his New York apartment.  Recorded by Michael Steinman for JAZZ LIVES (http://www.jazzlives.wordpress.com).
